desc: PetCount™ is a home test for measuring a dogs's sperm quality. It measures the concentration of Progressive Motile Sperm Cells per mL in its ejaculate, which are the only sperm cells that can reach and fertilize an egg in a natural way. PetCount™ gives you a true picture of your male dog's fertility potential.

layout.text: THE WORLD’S FIRST HOME TEST FOR DOGS USED BY VETS AND PRIVATE USERS THAT MEASURES DOG’S SPERM QUALITY.
